<author>Patea</author>
<title>Lau Kiu Inla Ngai un !</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lau kiu inla, ngai zaw tiem u mi cheng adi'n,
 Chanchin pha kipahum mah mah ka hun tun hi;
 Tunin nangu din David khuo ah Hukdampa a pieng,
 Lal Krista chu na tiemteh na'ng un'
 Gan kuong achun mun lau.

[V2]
 Ka Lal zanchamna mun aw ka ngai na lawm lawm e,
 Belampu zuia chieh ka nuom Bethlehem tang chunga
 Nausen puona tuom chu aw, dawngin eihilh theileh,
 A siem Zion khawpi tuolnuom chu,
 Ngailo thei puona.

[V3]
 2. Maa kipahna pak gimlim a tuoi zo tai,
 Mahleh ka Lalpa'n Zion pak hawih ei pe tai;
 Gamgaw gam hinle la sau hen &quot;Hossana&quot; tiin,
 Khawvel gam cheng chunga kipahna,
 Chamna thu leng viel hen.

[V4]
 3. Tang leh muol, pak tin kipak un van Hossana,
 Thiemgau gen bangin Zion dawngkawt a hun hawng;
 Van khawpi dingin lungkhamna leh luonthi nulna,
 Mahleh ei din phaicham zingtinpak,
 Hawih a hung lun kit tai.

[V5]
 4. Eden tuol ahung hawih kit tai, gal a bei tai,
 Kipahna gimlim leh van la hawih a leng viel;
 Kipak takin chawian hitiu I Lal liengvai hi,
 Ei hehpih bek ziekin eihaw din,
 Vankhaw lunlai a chan.</lyrics>
</song>